**Vulnerability: Staking Time Reset on Additional Deposits**

When a user calls `stake()` again to add more tokens, `stakeTime[msg.sender]` is reset to `block.timestamp`, erasing the accrued reward time on their *existing* stake. A user who staked 100 tokens for 30 days and then adds 1 more token loses all 30 days of accrued rewards on their original stake.

